{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just weeks, because the [INAUDIBLE]-- and I like to use the people's names in case their relatives are still out there, they should know-- and Mr.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maletski-- that name will come up again later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maletski had become suspicious by some new plaster in contrast to the old plaster along the attic wall, which is where-- behind which the little unit was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although it wasn't that new-- it wasn't like last week's plaster-- it looked different to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he brought the Gestapo up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Gestapo-- by Gestapo, I always mean plainclothesmen, no uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were sitting and eating our food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was our turn to eat at this little table.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And suddenly, it was complete silence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we heard, [GERMAN], which is an improper way of talking German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, it's worse than colloquial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's grammatically-- and in that country, you're judged by how you speak, still to this day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It meant, 'here, somewhere, is where they must be.' So we heard that, and we stopped eating.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were just quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Levents were in their little room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had the somewhat larger room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were little cots on which we slept.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And everyone just stood stock still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was still daylight, I remember, because during the daylight, we could take-- let some of the regular light in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the next thing we know, there's a shot, because the hiding place-- the attic-- had not only the wardrobe way of getting in with a clad iron door-- or a steel door-- with a lock at the very bottom of it, which we kept locked when we were in.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It would take some effort for them to break that down.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
